{
  "stem": "13981.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a sense of getting even.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had no feeling of being against my countrymen, you know, against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was complete-- it was a sense of getting even for what had happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we went through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our unit had to break through the Siegfried line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, another incident, one of the pictures that I have will show you, where my friend and I were in a dugout.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our captain had been in that dugout too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that particular day I had asked for permission to go up near the front lines, to get a better picture of what was going on so we could interrogate better.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And while I was gone, our captain got hit, got wounded by-- in-- in that very dugout.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So of course I didn't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the Regimental Commander came by and said, hey, what in the hell are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I said, I had permission to come up here and see what you're--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, you get your ass back over there where you belong.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Captain Woods got hurt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, of course-- [LAUGHS] --I did it immediately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I had not known about his being wounded.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But pardon my English.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our division was, but not I.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The division as a whole, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The division consists of three regiments.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was in one of the regiments.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, you know, it's subdivided.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It goes like a pyramid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the 409th Division.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not I.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't really know whether the-- the-- the front line, let's call it, the-- the-- the-- the lower echelons way up there were involved.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
